   - Configuration files
   - Build scripts
   is licensed under the MIT License. See LICENSE file for details.

2. Data License (CC BY-SA 3.0)
   All data files, including but not limited to:
   - Fortune cookie content in 'cookies/' directory
   - Processed and raw data
   - Curated collections
