   See LICENSE-DATA file for details.

Attribution Requirements:

For code usage:
- Include the MIT License notice
- Include this NOTICE file
- Attribute the Fortune Data Collection Project

For data usage:
- Provide appropriate attribution to the Fortune Data Collection Project
- Include a link to the CC BY-SA 3.0 license
- Indicate if changes were made
- Maintain the ShareAlike requirement by sharing any derivative works under the same license
- When using specific content, also attribute the original sources as listed in LICENSE-DATA

Third-Party Content:
This project includes content from various third-party sources, each maintaining their own license terms. See LICENSE-DATA for details about specific data sources and their attribution requirements.

Note on Data Sources:
The fortune cookie data in this project is derived from various public sources. While we make this derived work available under CC BY-SA 3.0, users should be aware that individual source materials may have their own terms of use. We encourage users to review and comply with the original source terms when using specific content.
